name: Dirty Men 2013 Fitness Men Calendar
description:
The promotions are up.... #DIRTYMENCALENDAR 2013 Are you ready to purchase your copy? 

Calendars are available for purchase through Calendar REPs. December 25, 2012 thru January 5th. After the January 8th all calendars will be available online throughout next year. They are 8.5 x 11 calendars

Promotional Video:

Featured in Video is the Construction worker, the Personal trainer, Dr D, The Cheater, American Gansta, the Sanitation Worker, the Football player, and the LumberJack. This is a Diverse calendar (hidden months are treats)....... http://youtu.be/xB60F-tVDqA

To find a city Rep near you (New York, NY, Charlotte, NC, Atlanta, GA, Tampa and Jacksonville, Fl) like the facebook page (http://www.facebook.com/DirtyMenCalendar) and leave a comment saying "I WANT THIS CALENDAR ASAP" and a designated rep will reply within 24 hours.
